://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paperless_office\">paperittomana organisaationa</a></em>.</p>\n<p>Asiakkainamme on kuntia sekä kotimaisia että ulkomaisia yrityksiä.</p>\n<p>Ohjelmistotuotannon ohella yrityksessämme on Linux-palvelinympäristöjen erikoisosaamista. Kaikki palvelimemme sijaitsevat Suomessa.</p>\n<p>Kuten moni muu projektimme, myös tämä sivusto <a href=\"https://github.com/Hypernova-Oy/WordPress/tree/hypernova\">on julkaistu GitHubissa</a>.</p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Etusivu','','publish','closed','open','','hypernova','','','2019-01-24 14:29:42','2019-01-24 14:29:42','',0,'http://homepage/?page_id=33',0,'page','',0),(34,1,'2018-12-19 14:21:32','2018-12-19 14:21:32','','Hypernova','','inherit','closed','closed','','33-revision-v1','','','2018-12-19 14:21:32','2018-12-19 14:21:32','',33,'http://homepage/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(36,1,'2018-12-19 14:24:22','2018-12-19 14:24:22','<p>Our products</p>\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Toveri</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>lol</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->','Hypernova','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2018-12-19 14:24:22','2018-12-19 14:24:22','',2,'http://homepage/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(38,1,'2018-12-19 14:28:29','2018-12-19 14:28:29','<strong>Hypernova Oy</strong> is a Finnish Software Development company. Our focus is on modern, open source software.','','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2018-12-19 14:28:29','2018-12-19 14:28:29','',2,'http://homepage/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(40,1,'2018-12-19 14:32:15','2018-12-19 14:32:15','<strong>Hypernova Oy</strong> is a Finnish Software Development company. Our focus is on modern, open source 